column5: Thinking rice lake. Anyone else plan on bearing the winds tomorrow? I haven't been out once yet and the boats been ready for a month!

Just go. Rice has been great!  I'd join you, but I plan on being out there with my son anyways.  I'm not sure how this cold and wind are going to effect the fish, but last time I was out (thurs) they were on fire!!  Husky jerks, taildancers, ans bucktail jigs all caught lots of fish.  S.
I was thinking about it. Was out last week with out the best results. Would like to go with someone that could show me a thing or two. Have a boat or would go with some one else.
Are you going after pickerel? Can I get in on this?
I was. Work begged me to come In. I said yes, regret that decision
